title: NBA Dunk Week with SBNation's Harrison Faigen
itunes:title: NBA Dunk Week with SBNation's Harrison Faigen
description:
Miles and Jack were pleased to be joined by SBNation's NBA Editor and co-host of the Silver Screen and Roll and Rewind and Reconsider podcasts, Harrison Faigen for the latest episode. They discussed the latest Westbrook rumors as well as taking a look back at some of the best dunks of the season. The episode also features a 1-on-1 between Jack and Coach Jim O'Brien about the lasting legacy of the late, great Bill Russell.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
